ome.smuggler.core.msg

Class ChannelMessage<M,D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.msg.ChannelMessage<M,D>

  • public class ChannelMessage<M,D>
extends java.lang.Object
    Imposes a minimal structure to a message exchanged on a channel. This represents a common use case where the data to be consumed by the receiving end is possibly accompanied by metadata. Typically metadata is used to configure the sending of a message and/or to specify additional message properties.
